metadata.name: Council of Nicks Membership Card
metadata.description:
The Council of Nicks is established by Nicks, for Nicks. This exclusive Council of Nicks Membership Card grants access to the Network of Nicks, a growing conglomerate of leaders of many diverse backgrounds and professionals in their respective fields. Nicks help Nicks. 

Nick Champange is a mentor to many and a student of life. His saga continues around the world. This NFT immortalizes the legend. 


Welcome to the Council of Nicks.
